# Currency Exchange Service

This service provides an API to get the current USD to UAH exchange rate
and to subscribe to email notifications about the exchange rate.

## API Endpoints

### GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/rate
Returns the current USD to UAH exchange rate.

### POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/subscribe
Subscribes an email address to daily notifications about the exchange rate.

## In config.py  you need to insert  corect values in class Config.

You can use the test OPENEXCHANGERATES_API_KEY = "dacee103637befefa0104478"
or create your own at https://app.exchangerate-api.com/dashboard/confirmed.
## RUN
```  docker compose up --build ```
